Enum SqlType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<SqlType>
      • org.apache.calcite.avatica.SqlType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<SqlType>

    public enum SqlType
extends Enum<SqlType>
    Extends the information in Types.

    The information in the following conversions tables (from the JDBC 4.1 specification) is held in members of this class.
